'''馬里迪'''是[[南蘇丹|南蘇丹]]西南部的小鎮，由[[西赤道省|西赤道省]]負責管轄，位於首都[[朱巴|朱巴]]以西約295公里<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Sudan_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Juba%20()%20(Airport)&toplace=Maridi%20(Al%20Wilayah%20al%20Istiwa'iyah)&fromlat=4.872006&tolat=4.9147222&fromlng=31.601117&tolng=29.4769444 |title=Map Showing Juba And Maridi With Distance Marker |access-date=2011-09-11 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205028/http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Sudan_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Juba%20()%20(Airport)&toplace=Maridi%20(Al%20Wilayah%20al%20Istiwa'iyah)&fromlat=4.872006&tolat=4.9147222&fromlng=31.601117&tolng=29.4769444 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，毗鄰與[[剛果民主共和國|剛果民主共和國]]接壤的邊界，鎮上有機場設施，2011年人口約18,000<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://sisp-sudan.com/?pname=open&f=doc100855_newspik046a_to03_250px.jpg&id=855&type=html |title=Estimated Population In 2011 |access-date=2011-09-11 |archive-date=2012-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120326191430/https://sisp-sudan.com/?pname=open&f=doc100855_newspik046a_to03_250px.jpg&id=855&type=html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

